  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting the development of teacher training in science and technology for sustainable development</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The activity contributes to the regional implementation of TVET according to agenda E2030 and the regional roadmap for its implementation, by helping reinforces teachers training institutes in science and technology. Technical assistance will be provided to the development of policies in the training and continuing education of teachers in science and technology, in line with the regional strategy for teachers. Moreover, this activity reinforces Montevideo Office&apos;s work on science education. Emphasis will be equally placed on policies that favor subject areas with the most acute shortage of qualified teachers (mathematics, science, engineering and technology), especially for girls and women, and on harnessing the potential of ICTs for teaching and learning.</narrative>
  </description>
